<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Greasy" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Greasy,</orth> 1) smeared, defiled with grease: <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.5.92" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 5, 92</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.55" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 2, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.252" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 252</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 5.2.159" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 2, 159</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 4.6.131" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. IV, 6, 131</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.210" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. V, 2, 210</bibl>.<lb />2) fat, bulky, corpulent: <cit><quote>this g. knight,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.1.112" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 1, 112</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>g. Joan doth keel the pot,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.930" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 930</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.930" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 930</bibl> <cit><quote>you fat and g. citizens,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.1.55" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 1, 55</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>